name: Name
text: §421-5  Name.  Section 414D-61 shall apply to associations formed under this chapter and no domestic corporation not organized under this chapter shall use the word "cooperative" as a part of its name. [L 1949, c 234, pt of §1; am L 1953, c 137, §1(c); RL 1955, §176-6; HRS §421-5; am L 1983, c 167, §11(1); am L 1985, c 270, §4; am L 1988, c 370, §3; am L 2001, c 129, §62; am L 2002, c 40, §56]
